# {{projectName}}

Full-stack application with Rust Axum backend and React TypeScript frontend.

## Architecture

```
{{projectName}}/
├── backend/ # Rust Axum API
│ ├── src/
│ └── Cargo.toml
├── frontend/ # React TypeScript SPA
│ ├── src/
│ └── package.json
├── docker-compose.yml
└── Makefile
```

## Prerequisites

- Rust {{rustVersion}}+
- Node.js {{nodeVersion}}+
- pnpm 9+
- cargo-watch (for hot reload): `cargo install cargo-watch`

## Quick Start

### Install Dependencies

```bash
pnpm install
```

### Development

Run both backend and frontend:

```bash
make dev
```

Or run separately:

```bash
# Backend only (http://localhost:{{backendPort}})
make dev-backend

# Frontend only (http://localhost:{{frontendPort}})
make dev-frontend
```

### Build

```bash
make build
```

### Test

```bash
make test
```

{{#if enableDocker}}
## Docker

```bash
make docker-build
make docker-up
```
{{/if}}

